OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSome warm sunny spells
OL,6,Fexpected, but with cloud building to
OL,7,Fbring occasional showers, heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes. However some areas will stay
OL,9,Fdry, most likely along southern
OL,10,Fcoasts. Winds becoming light.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOften
OL,13,Fcloudy Friday, with the odd shower,
OL,14,Fbut also some brighter spells. Rain
OL,15,Flikely Saturday morning, clearing to
OL,16,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier, and
OL,17,Fsunnier Sunday with winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
